thread.title: Kenneth Wilson
thread.title_full: Omni Financial reviewed by Kenneth Wilson

author: Kenneth Wilson
title: Kenneth Wilson
text: I was very pleased with the professional and honest service that I received from Stacey Gill. This is the second time that I have contracted with Omni Financial to remedy an IRS tax problem. On both occasions, I was completely satisfied with the outcome. I would recommend Omni Financial, without reservation, to all my friends and anyone requiring financial assistance.
